Functions of this module handle private and shared sync lock allocation, free and access.

TYPE urt_sem: opaque
	A type representing a semaphore

	A type representing a semaphore. The actual type depends on the real-time back-end.

FUNCTION urt_sem_new: (init_value: unsigned int): urt_sem *
	Create a new semaphore

	This function creates and returns a new semaphore. This semaphore is unnamed and cannot be shared with other processes.

	INPUT init_value
		Initial value of the semaphore
	OUTPUT
		A new semaphore, or `NULL` if not possible.
